" Toggle Toolbars
nmap ,<left> :xccmd toggleNavigatorsVisibility<CR>
nmap ,<down> :xccmd toggleDebuggerVisibility<CR>
nmap ,<right> :xccmd toggleUtilitiesVisibility<CR>

nmap ,. :xccmd jumpToNextCounterpart<CR>
nmap ,j :xccmd jumpToDefinition<CR>
nmap ,c :xcmenucmd Find Call Hierarchy<CR>

" fold
nnoremap zc :xccmd fold<cr>
nnoremap zo :xccmd unfold<cr>

" search under cursor
map ,k viw:xccmd findSelectedTextInWorkspace<CR>

map ,, :xcmenucmd Show Document Items<CR>
map ,r :xcmenucmd Show Related Items<CR>

nmap > >>
nmap < <<

" Other key binding by setting Xcode directly
" ctrl + o: open quickly
" cmd + ]: go forward
" cmd + [: go back
" cmd + enter: go to next focus area
" cmd + f: find
" cmd + shift + f: find in project
" option + mouse click: open document
